            <p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="1">I don't know about that.  Killing level 45ish stuff in Skyfire last night with my warrior seemed pretty trivial, and those mobs are supposedly tough for their level.  With no haste or slows or buffs except aegolism, I was taking 1-2 bubbles health per kill, which is easily bandaged up.  I'm out of touch with the end game these days, but it seems to me that warriors who have never raided in their lives have better equipment than my warrior these days, given the kind of stuff that is now purchasable.  It seems to me that soloing weaker level 45 mobs like LDC's ought to be trivial for most level 60 melees today.</font></p>
             
